(0, 'U r my Fatabetiee &#10084;&#65039;', 'Hemamalini', 'Damaram', 'Helping tendency and caring&#10084;&#65039;\r\nSelflessness in studies\r\nEtc etc&#128520;', 'College \r\nCollege \r\nCollege \r\nNamma Room la&#10084;&#65039;', 'Then - scene party\r\nNow - If life(clg) is rain,you are my raincoat&#128153;\r\n\r\nVery very important person in my clg life\r\n\r\nEnoda clg lyf la enoda survival kit especially third and final la...nee and kural illana...antha two years epdi irunthurukum nu enaku thrla..romba lonely ah feel pannirupen...but neenga antha maari enna feel pannama paathukitinga...you are very very special to me&#10084;&#65039;', '\r\nNeraya tym kovam vanthuruku.\r\n\r\nNee normal la pannuva...but enaku kovam varum...aprm pesnathum seri aagidum..so prblm illa &#128556;\r\n \r\nAnd\r\n \r\nIppa enaku yethu neyabagam varala&#128546;&#128582;\r\nAthan ipdila samalikuren&#129315;\r\nNeyabagam vantha solren&#128520;\r\n\r\n', 'Char - inum apdi oru muv varalaya..illa nan paakalaya thrla&#128582;\r\n \r\nMy al tym supporter &#128153;\r\n Sometimes nee panrathu pidikathu \r\n Sometimes pidikum\r\n Ipdi oru char.. yethachu unaku therinja sollu', 'Thief&#128514;\r\n \r\n\r\nYethachu thirudi maatirupa&#129315;', 'Unkitta already superpower iruku&#129488;\r\nNan enna koduka&#129300;\r\n\r\n\r\nLifelong enoda sister ah Iruka maari superpower tharuven.\r\nBcoz ellame enaku neeye panniduva..ippayum apdi dan pannitu iruka...\r\nEg..proj assignment yetha irunthalum ne dan enaku panra...athan\r\nEnaku nee neraya panniruka madhu...but nan athuka olunga thank panrana and olunga response panranu kuda enaku thrla..enaku therinju nan olunga thank pannathu illa..even antha photo frame ku kuda nan olunga respond pannananu thrla enaku...enaku guilty ah vey irukum..but athuku reason serious ah ve enaku epdi thank pannanum nu thrla....neraya matter la nee enaku help panniruka...later ah dan thonum...madhu ku thank pannirukanum...Namma olunga response pannalaye nu...but nee athella edthum serious ah eduthukama..enkitta normal la irupa..same caring oda...ippa kuda enaku epdi thank pannanum nu thrla..but nan thonuratha solren.\r\nThanks a ton maaadyy galll&#10084;&#65039; for each and everything &#10084;&#65039; from first yr to now&#10084;&#65039;', 'Nan unaku enga enga respond pannanuma proper ah..apdi la pannuven&#10084;&#65039;\r\nCrct dan thank pannuven&#10084;&#65039;', 'Ella exam um orey naal la vaika solli pass panniduven&#128514; serious ah intha maari dan yethachu pannuven...studies related ah&#128556;\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Yessss....neraya matter ku..again athan olunga respond pannathathuku dan..\r\n\r\nEnaku epovum thonum..nee enna care panra maari..nan unna panrathu illanu..athuku sorry kepen&#129402;', 'Yyyyyyyeeeeeeessssssssssssss&#10084;&#65039;\r\n\r\nNeraya moment la&#10084;&#65039; \r\n\r\n From caption solrathula irunthu care panra varaikum&#128153;\r\nAnd studies definitely u r my backbone&#10084;&#65039;\r\n\r\nAprm sek matter la&#128514; jff&#129315;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n Especially intha leave la...each and every moment feel panren yen nu thrla&#128514;&#10084;&#65039;', 'Mela oru thathuvam solliruken poi paaru&#128556;\r\n\r\nYou are my raincoat&#10084;&#65039;\r\n\r\nI LOVE YOU TO THE MOON AND BACK&#10084;&#65039;\r\nVirtual Hugs to you&#129395;\r\n\r\nMissinggg you badly &#129402;&#10084;&#65039;', '8270265958'),
(0, 'Same birthday date but different month &#9829;&#65039;&#9829;&#65039;, ur blacky!&#128514;&#128514;&#128514;&#128514;', 'Keerthana', 'Bulky ', 'Evlo kashtathulayum enaku help pannum nenjam.....\r\n\r\nPartiality paakama palagurathu\r\n\r\nTrustworthy ever.supportive ..understandingg..', 'Lets get on with our helmets in a two wheeler and go all around chennai....or group study where i ll be sitting next to u and chatting and u ll be beating me and scolding and teaching me!', 'Yaraa ivaa...loosu maari suthitu irikaa vaaya thorantha moodave maatra\r\n\r\nMy bulky! One person i would rely upon to cry or to blabber or to share anything ...\r\n\r\nIpo ipa epo aanalum...\r\n\" Madhu irukaa enaku ethunalum help panuva ena pathukuva\"\r\n\r\n', 'Exam tension la irukapa comedy panuva...apo gandagum avlo tha', 'Ithu thaanga enaku romba pudicha questionn\r\n\r\n1.Tun tun aunty from chota beam\r\n2.mala 2.0 (not movie but college character)\r\n', 'Ena panirpaa...aduthava snacks ah thirudeerpa....ilana pasi thangama gurunath aah adichu nasam akirpa..or canteen la chola puri nala ilana master aah kola panirpa (pinkurupi: nala ilatha chola puriyayum saptutu tha kola panirpa...and also gurunath ah galli panitu tha adutha vela start panirpa)', 'Slim fit aagra power....ava ishtam pola baloon maari venngikalam..ila tamana maari oli aagi belly dance aadalam...ava wish ku etha maari antha power vela seiyum...', 'I ll go back to my first year..and would have become friends with u.....miss paniten madhu serious aah&#9785;&#65039;', 'Naane nala tha sapduven aaana mood off ana tha avlo sapduven...so madhu maari full tym aah saptutu irupen..foodieee&#129303;&#129303;&#129303;', 'Sorry for annoying u during studies madhu reallly .....\r\nIpdi la soluven nu kanavula kooda ethirpakatha....na torture pannuven ne poruthu tha poganum..&#128540;\r\n\r\nSo the real apology is ...\r\nSorry for not becoming friends in first sem itself&#128534;', 'Alwayss and also forever!\r\n\r\n\r\nthe day when i