(0, 'Your only dayscholar friend. You sometime call me as servlet ......', 'Nisha', 'Madhu ', 'Your childish character and your speaking style and very helful. Ready to help anytime', 'I wish there would should never exist such a day. If so i would like to meet you in our college hostel and staying with all of u for atleast one night and innonu namba summer intern days.', 'Nee rmba marana topper ah irupa nu nenaichen konjam serious nu nenaichen. Now totally different from what i thought rmba jolly type , childish and your speaking style is what i admire the most ', 'Apdilam edhum illa idhu varaikum apdi kovam vandhadhe illa ', 'Unakkum enakkum la vara trisha oda character en nu theriyadhu but ava pesradhu panra actions lam ennaku konjam nee resemble panra mari irukum', 'Oru padathula varum la nayanthara dog mela stone potu jail ku poiduva neeyum andha mari pannita nu nenaipen&#128517;', 'Unakku time travel power kudupen. So that nee marubadiyum unnoda happy moments ah relive pannalam.', 'I will go back to the first year of our college life and our summer internship days&#128525;&#128525;', 'Apdi maruna i will try to fill happiness wherever i am like you do always.Ana nee topper vera ya ennala unna mari doubts lam clear panna mudiyadhu solliyum thara theriyadhu. Adhuku better neeye madhu va irukradhu dhan&#128517;&#128517;', 'Yes neraya time nee enna veliya kooptruka sila time ennala vara mudila adhuku dhan sorry. In case nan edhachum theriyama eppo achum unna hurt pannirundha i m really sorry for it.', 'Yes kandippa i m really glad that i m in your life. illana oru semma nalla friend nan miss pannirpen. Maina exam time appo lam nee solli tharala na padhi xam pass eh pannirka maten&#128517;', 'You are one good person whom i dont want to miss in my life. You are one who made my college life so special and awesome. Inga kedaicha memories lam eppoyum marakka matten maina andha summer intern lam chance illa thirumba indha mari happy memories lam kedaikuma therila theatre, canteen , aprm last day andha zoo ku ponome adhellam chance illa. Maybe nan hostel la irundha un kooda innum neraya time spend pannirkalam nu kashtama irukum. Nee different different ah name kudukradhu lam ennaku rmba pidikum nee pesradhu ellame. But college mudiya pogudhu nu nala rmba kashtama irukum i m really going to miss u. Pls eppome touch la iru enga ponalum marakka koodadhu. Luv u too the core&#9829;&#65039;&#9829;&#65039; and will miss u very badly.', '7395936543'),
