(0, 'My birthday is on sept 19, your mamiyar,non-sync thotti&#128556;!', 'Jaya barathi', 'Dolabula', 'Epa enna situation laium eathu kettalum ignore pannama illa nu sollama pandrathu , help pandra tendancy, care pandrathu, great advisor.', 'College la veliya engaiyavathu poitu oru nal fullah suthitu njoy pannitu saptu photo eadukanum! miss you!eager to meet you!', 'First impression um Seri current impression um athe than!ne epavu oru positive vibes mathiri than!evolo kavalaiya feel pannitu iruthalum ne athuku arthal soldrathu advise pandrathu nambalala mudium ipa try panna kuda apidinu soldrathulam apidi ye manasa nalla feel Panna vekkum!irutha bayam um poidum!', 'Oru sila times enna vechi cmdy ah pesarappa angry ayduven ana aprm nengathanu fun pandriganu antha angry poidum&#10084;&#65039;!', 'Resembles like Hashini&#128517;&#10084;&#65039;!', 'Mess la iruthu egg token eaduthathuku aprm class la iruthu pen eaduthathuku&#128514;&#10084;&#65039;!', 'Mind reading&#128514;&#10084;&#65039;!', 'If there is a time Machine I can travel back in time to the date first day we have met. I juz want to feel the same now.', 'If I were you I will be someone\'s positive vibes like you and make others laugh. Athukapparo unna mathiri entha situation laium help pandra tendancy.', 'Yes.\r\nI need to apologize for broken your trust on me for the first time in 3rd year. Sorry&#10084;&#65039;!', 'I am glad to have you in my life. I really cherish each and every moment spent with you.Just keep smiling like this always. I love you madho&#10084;&#65039;.', 'You are like a positive energy, a higher vibration. when you\'re around , you make all of them laugh with ur funny talks. Keep this always. you are important to me because you just the way you are and I feel comfortable with you. ', '9442639072'),
