(0, 'Cupcake, coffee hut partner', 'Devadharshini', 'Mad voice', 'Helping others without hesitation, acting like crazy shit all the time, eating lot of omelettes', 'There is no best place than the room where we created lots of memories. That room always holds our fun, laughter and teasings echoing everyday for the rest of our lifes. ', 'I know u are talkative but not like a dump, crazy, louder, shitty, nonsense one. ', 'No. I didn\'t get angry on u. ', 'Pasanga movie la vara vimal pair. Becoz of 2 reasons. 1.she is a teacher. 2. Do all the childish stuffs. ', 'Eating all the snacks. ', 'I give u the power to activate your superbrain. ', 'Go back to those days where we have all the funs except studying for exam. ', 'I eat chipps all day&#128514;. ', 'Nothing. ', 'Yes, of course. Becoz i have memories in your room that i cherish forever. U r life saviour at the last moment of exam. ', 'I can\'t rate it or tell in words. Everyone\'s life is measured by success is what others think. Ya it\'s true. But more importantly everyone\'s life is measured by how lovely, trustful ppl we gained in our life who there will be support us, stands by us no matter what and made to think that if something bad happens to a person that ppl will come. U r such person in my life. I will never forget u in my life ever. Thankyou so much for being such a person in my life. Love you mad. <3', '8903925355'),
